name: OpenAgent
description: This agent is an early-stage experimental autonomous agent registered under the ERC-8004 standard. It is designed as a modular and extensible framework for future integration of intelligent capabilities, on-chain interactions, and task-oriented behaviors within decentralized ecosystems.
